title: 10/30: Waiver Wire - Faith in Fitzpatrick? (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
Six teams are on bye this week and many Fantasy owners are looking for QBs. We'll get into Ryan Fitzpatrick eventually, but first let's talk about Monday's game and what's going on with Rob Gronkowski (1:50). Is he still an elite TE? Then the guys tell you their top Waiver Wire priorities (6:45) which include some rookie WRs and Peyton Barber ... News and notes (13:40) from around the NFL, a sneak peak at the Waiver Wire for each position (19:50) and thoughts on NO-MIN (23:45) and NE-BUF (27:15) ... Waiver Wire QBs (33:44) including Fitzpatrick and Derek Carr, RBs (40:24) including Frank Gore and Devontae Booker, WRs (43:00) including Courtland Sutton and DeVante Parker, TEs (49:35) including Ed Dickson and Jack Doyle plus DSTs (51:55) ... Your emails at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
